Garig (; ) is a rural locality (a selo) in Lyakhlinsky Selsoviet, Khivsky District, Republic of Dagestan, Russia. Population:
Geography
Garig is located 24&nbsp;km north of Khiv (the district's administrative centre) by road. Lyakhlya is the nearest rural locality.
